Class CenyService

java.lang.Object
com.project.springbootjavafx.services.AbstractServices<Ceny,Integer>
com.project.springbootjavafx.services.CenyService
@Service public class CenyService extends AbstractServices<Ceny,Integer>
The CenyService class provides service methods for managing pricing information (represented by the Ceny entity) in the application.

It extends AbstractServices to inherit common CRUD operations and additional functionality. This service allows adding new pricing records and retrieving pricing information based on a given trip type.

    • findByTypWycieczki

      public Ceny findByTypWycieczki(TypyWycieczek typ)
      Retrieves pricing information for the specified trip type.

      This method retrieves a Ceny entity based on the trip type by calling CenyRepository.findByTypWycieczki(String). If the provided trip type is null, an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.

      Parameters:
      typ - the TypyWycieczek instance representing the trip type
      Returns:
      the Ceny entity corresponding to the specified trip type
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the provided trip type is null
